     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: List ExampleSubmissionSet</b></p><a name=\"ExampleSubmissionSet\"> </a><a name=\"hcExampleSubmissionSet\"> </a><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\"/><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profile: <a href=\"StructureDefinition-pdsm-submissionset-comprehensive.html\">PDSm SubmissionSet Comprehensive</a></p></div><h2>Dossier de suivi post-opératoire</h2><table class=\"clstu\"><tr><td>Date: 2025-04-30 14:00:00+0100 </td><td>Mode: Working List </td><td>Status: Current </td><td>Code: Submission Set </td></tr><tr><td>Subject: <a href=\"Patient-fr-patient-123.html\">Martin Claire  Male, DoB: 1980-01-15</a>Source: </td></tr></table><p>note</p><blockquote><div><p>Suivi post-chirurgical – documents cliniques regroupés.</p>\n</div></blockquote><table class=\"grid\"><tr style=\"backgound-color: #eeeeee\"><td><b>Items</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"DocumentReference-exemple-pdsm-documentreference.html\">DocumentReference: masterIdentifier = UUID:12345678-abcd-1234-abcd-1234567890ab (use: usual, ); status = current; type = Résumé de sortie d’hospitalisation; category = Compte-rendu; date = 2025-04-29 12:00:00+0100; description = Compte rendu d’hospitalisation suite à une chirurgie.; securityLabel = Normal</a></td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Contained Resources</b></p><hr/><a name=\"ExampleSubmissionSet/practitionerrole-example\"> </a><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>PractitionerRole #practitionerrole-example</b></p><a name=\"hcExampleSubmissionSet/practitionerrole-example\"> </a><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">version: 1; Last updated: 2025-04-28 18:19:34+0200; Language: fr;